# Walkthrough: Realtime Sync Engine — Errors Fixed

## What Was Done

All compilation errors in the Spring Boot realtime-sync-engine project have been resolved.
`mvnw.cmd clean compile` now reports **BUILD SUCCESS** with 20 source files compiled.

## Root Causes Found & Fixed

### 1. All Java Source Files Were Missing
The project had empty subdirectories but no Java code other than [RealtimeSyncEngineApplication.java](file:///c:/Users/BHAVESH/Downloads/realtime-sync-engine/realtime-sync-engine/src/main/java/com/sync/engine/RealtimeSyncEngineApplication.java).
All files were written from scratch:

