## To Run the Application

1. Start PostgreSQL with database `sync_engine`, user `postgres`, password `postgres`
2. From the project folder:
   ```
   .\mvnw.cmd spring-boot:run
   ```
3. Open: [http://localhost:8080](http://localhost:8080)
